msgid ""
"On the server side we will enable ``ComponentProtocol`` component as we "
"need to do to enable external component without clustering support."
msgstr ""

#: ../../Tigase_Admistration/Components/External_Component_Configuration/Load_Balancing.rst:31
msgid ""
